\c 37
\s Vanhu vaJehovha vachamutswa samapfupa akaoma
\p
\v 1 Ruoko rwaJehovha rwakanga ruri pamusoro pangu, akandibudisa noMweya waJehovha, akandondiisa pakati pomupata; iwo wakanga uzere namapfupa;
\v 2 akandipfuudza napakati pawo kumativi ose; tarirai, aivapo akawanda kwazvo pakachena pamupata; uye tarirai, akanga akaoma kwazvo.
\v 3 Akati kwandiri, "Mwanakomana, mapfupa awa angararama here?" Ndikapindura, ndikati, "Imi Ishe Jehovha munozviziva."
\p
\v 4 Zvino akatizve kwandiri, "Porofita pamusoro pamapfupa awa, uti kwaari, `Imi mapfupa akaoma, inzwai shoko raJehovha.'
\v 5 Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha kumapfupa awa, `Tarirai, ndichapinza mweya mukati menyu, muchararamazve.
\v 6 Ndichaisa marunda pamusoro pcnyu, nokuuyisa nyama pamusoro penyu, nokukufukidzai neganda, nokuisa mweya mukati menyu, murarame; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha.' "
\p
\v 7 Ipapo ndakaporofita sezvandakarayirwa; zvino ndakati ndichiporofita, mubvumo ukavapo, uye, tarira, kudengenyeka kwenyika kwakavapowo; mapfupa akaswederana, pfupa rimwe kune rimwe pfupa raro.
\v 8 Ndikatarira, wane marunda avapo pamusoro pawo, nyama ikauya, ganda rikaafukidza pamusoro payo; asi makanga musina mweya mukati mawo.
\p
\v 9 Ipapo akati kwandiri, "Porofitera kumhepo, porofita, Mwanakomana womunhu, uti kumhepo, zvanzi naIshe Jehovha, `Uya uchibva kumativi mana anobva mhepo, iwe mweya, ufuridzire pamusoro pavava vakaurawa, kuti vararame.' "
\p
\v 10 Ipapo ndakaporofita sezvaakandirayira, mweya ukapinda mukati mavo, vakararama, vakamira netsoka dzavo, iri hondo huru kwazvo.
\p
\v 11 Zvino akati kwandiri, "Mwanakomana womunhu, mapfupa awa ndiyo imba yose yaIsiraeri. Tarira ivo vanoti, `Mapfupa edu aoma, tariro yedu yaenda, taparadzwa chose.'
\v 12 Naizvozvo porofita, uti kwavari zvanzi naIshe Jehovha, `Tarirai, ndichazarura marinda enyu, ndichakukwidzai mubve mumarinda enyu, imi vanhu vangu; ndichakusvitsai munyika yaIsiraeri.
\v 13 Muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha, kana ndazarura marinda enyu, ndikakukwidzai mubve mumarinda enyu, imi vanhu vangu.
\v 14 Ndichaisa mweya wangu mukati menyu, murarame, ndichakuisai munyika yenyu; zvino muchaziva kuti ini Jehovha ndakazvitaura ndikazviita,' " ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 15 Shoko raJehovha rakasvikazve kwandiri, richiti,
\v 16 "Zvino iwe, Mwanakomana womunhu, tora rutanda rumwe, unyore pamusoro parwo, kuti, `ZvaJudha, nezvavana vaIsiraeri shamwari dzake;' ipapo utore rumwe rutanda, unyore pamusoro parwo, kuti, `ZvaJosefa, rutanda rwaEfuremu, nezveimba yose yavaIsiraeri shamwari dzake;'
\v 17 zvino uzvibatanidzire matanda iwawo, ruve rutanda rumwe, ruve rumwe muruoko rwako.
\v 18 Zvino kana vana vavanhu vako vakataura newe vachiti kwauri, `Haungatizivisi zvaunoda kuratidza nezvinhu izvi here?'
\v 19 Iwe uti kwavari, zvanzi naIshe Jehovha, `Tarirai, ndichatora rutanda rwaJosefa, ruri muruoko rwaEfuremu, namarudzi aIsiraeri shamwari dzake; ndichavaisa kwaruri, kurutanda rwaJudha, ndivaite rutanda rumwe, vachaita rumwe muruoko rwangu.'
\p
\v 20 "Zvino matanda aunonyora pamusoro pawo anofanira kuva muruoko rwako vazvione.
\v 21 Ipapo uti kwavari, zvanzi naIshe Jehovha, `Tarirai, ndichabvisa vana vaIsiraeri pakati pamarudzi, kwavakaenda, ndichavaunganidza vabve kumativi ose, ndivaise kunyika yavo;
\v 22 ndichavaita rudzi rumwe panyika, pamakomo aIsiraeri; mambo mumwe uchava mambo wavose, havangazovi marudzi maviri, uye havangatongozovi ushe huviri hwakaparadzana;
\v 23 havangazozvisvibisi nezvifananidzo zvavo, kana nezvinhu zvavo zvinosemesa, kana nechinhu chipi nechipi chavanodarika nacho; asi ndichavaponesa pose pavagere, pavaitadza, nokuvanatsa; saizvozvo vachava vanhu vangu, neni ndichava Mwari wavo.'
\p
\v 24 "Muranda wangu Dhavhidhi achava mambo wavo; vose vachava nomufudzi mumwe; vachafambawo nezvandakarayira, nokuchengeta mitemo yangu, vachiita.
\p
\v 25 "Vachagara munyika yandakapa Jakobho muranda wangu, maigara madzibaba enyu; vachagaramo, ivo navana vavo, navana vavana vavo, nokusingaperi; Dhavhidhi muranda wangu achava muchinda wavo nokusingaperi.
\v 26 Ndichaitawo sungano yorugare navo, ichava sungano isingaperi navo; ndichavaisapo, nokuvawanza, nokuisa nzvimbo yangu tsvene pakati pavo nokusingaperi.
\v 27 Tabhenakeri yanguvo ichava pakati pavo; ini ndichava Mwari wavo, naivo vachava vanhu vangu.
\v 28 Zvino marudzi achaziva kuti ndini Jehovha, anoita vaIsiraeri vatsvene, kana nzvimbo yangu tsvene iri pakati pavo nokusingaperi."
